<p>GDP growth: 2.4% GDP: $2.2bn (PPP: $2.4bn) Inflation: 9.1% Population: 12.6m GDP per head: $180 (PPP: $190)</p>

<p>Elections are likely in 2012, but, with many in Robert Mugabe's long-dominant party determined to prevent victory for its partner in the power-sharing government, “free and fair” will not come into it. Still, Mr Mugabe is old and ailing and could quit with little notice, unleashing a power struggle.</p>

